      "repair_reason": "Human review is required because this member PR has protected maintainer/human-review handling and the remaining blockers are security-sensitive proxy policy defects after automation was stopped.; Needs attention: The diff still leaves direct loopback routes where the new managed-proxy policy says traffic should be proxied or limited to the configured Gateway URL.; Review finding: [P1] Route inherited proxy-mode loo... (sha=b5e83f60a6aa435bfcb8be6feab93264e2871b6a)",
